# Documentation and Markdown Files
# Rationale: Documentation files are intentionally excluded from Prettier formatting to allow
# manual formatting control. This enables:
# - Custom table formatting for better readability
# - Intentional line breaks and spacing in documentation
# - Preservation of carefully structured lists and hierarchies
# - Compatibility with various markdown renderers that have different formatting preferences
# Decision: Keep exclusions to maintain documentation quality and author control
/docs
*.md

